Package com.akmal.springfoodieappbackend.mapper

Class MenuItemMapper

java.lang.Object
com.akmal.springfoodieappbackend.mapper.MenuItemMapper
public abstract class MenuItemMapper extends Object
Class represents a contract based on which Mapstruct library generates the mapper class at runtime. Converts MenuItem Object to DTO and vice versa.
